      +projectTitle(
        {title:"HIV TEST APPLICATION",
        titleDes:"Oraquick is an in-home HIV oral test kit for users to get HIV test results within 30 mins. But it might have false results which lead to bad product reviews. We designed the digital product for Oraquick to reduce the complaints by providing clear instructions and further assistance for the user with a positive result.",
